SEC Sues UBS Financial Services Over Securities

-- B y   D a v i d   E .   R o v e l l a
-- 
2011-05-04T19:09:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/sec-sues-ubs-financial-services-over-securities-correct-.html
(Corrects to say bidding in first paragraph.)  The U.S. Securities and Exchange
Commission sued UBS Financial Services Inc. over alleged
fraudulent bidding practices involving tax-exempt municipal
securities and at least 100 transactions, according to a court
filing today in New Jersey federal court.  To contact the reporter on this story:
